.TH DESI-CLI 1 "May 2026" "1.0.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
desi\-cli \- browse, stream, and download Indian movies and TV series
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B desi\-cli
[options] [query]
.br
.B desi\-cli
[query] [options]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Browse, stream, and download Bollywood, Marathi, Tamil, Telugu, Malayalam,
Kannada, Bengali, and Punjabi movies and TV series from the terminal.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BR \-c ", " \-\-continue
Continue watching from history.
.TP
.BR \-d ", " \-\-download
Download media instead of playing.
.TP
.BR \-D ", " \-\-delete
Delete watch history.
.TP
.BR \-l ", " \-\-language " <lang>"
Language filter. Supported values: all, hindi, marathi, tamil, telugu,
malayalam, kannada, bengali, punjabi.
.TP
.BR \-p ", " \-\-provider " <provider>"
Source provider. Supported: youtube, url.
.TP
.BR \-q ", " \-\-quality " <quality>"
Specify quality (720p, 1080p, best, worst).
.TP
.BR \-v ", " \-\-vlc
Use VLC instead of mpv.
.TP
.BR \-s ", " \-\-syncplay
Use Syncplay for synchronized viewing.
.TP
.BR \-S ", " \-\-select\-nth " <n>"
Select the nth search result directly (non\-interactive).
.TP
.BR \-e ", " \-\-episode " <n>"
Episode number (for series).
.TP
.BR \-r ", " \-\-range " <start-end>"
Episode range (e.g., 1\-10).
.TP
.BR \-\-season " <n>"
Season number (default: 1).
.TP
.BR \-\-url " <URL>"
Direct URL (YouTube, Einthusan, or any yt\-dlp\-supported site).
.TP
.BR \-\-cookies\-file " <file>"
Path to a cookies.txt file for YouTube authentication.
.TP
.BR \-V ", " \-\-version
Show version number.
.TP
.BR \-h ", " \-\-help
Show help message.
.TP
.BR \-U ", " \-\-update " [branch]"
Update the script. Optionally specify a git branch.
.TP
.BR \-\-rofi
Use rofi instead of fzf.
.TP
.BR \-\-dmenu
Use dmenu instead of fzf.
.TP
.BR \-\-no\-detach
Don't detach player (for in\-terminal playback).
.TP
.BR \-\-exit\-after\-play
Exit after playing (non\-interactive mode).
.TP
.BR \-\-debug
Print debug information.
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
Search and play a movie:
desi\-cli sholay
.TP
Search with language filter:
desi\-cli \-l marathi duniyadari
.TP
Direct URL playback:
desi\-cli \-\-url https://einthusan.tv/movie/watch/example/
.TP
Watch a TV series episode:
desi\-cli \-l hindi \-e 1 sacred games
.TP
Download in 1080p:
desi\-cli \-d \-q 1080p RRR
.TP
Resume from history:
desi\-cli \-\-continue
.TP
Use cookies for YouTube authentication:
desi\-cli \-\-cookies\-file cookies.txt \-\-url <url>
.SH ENVIRONMENT
.TP
.B DESI_CLI_PLAYER
Player command (default: auto\-detected).
.TP
.B DESI_CLI_DOWNLOAD_DIR
Download directory (default: current directory).
.TP
.B DESI_CLI_QUALITY
Default quality (default: best).
.TP
.B DESI_CLI_LANG
Default language filter (default: all).
.TP
.B DESI_CLI_PROVIDER
Default provider (default: auto).
.TP
.B DESI_CLI_NO_DETACH
Don't detach player (default: 0).
.TP
.B DESI_CLI_EXIT_AFTER_PLAY
Exit after playing (default: 0).
.TP
.B DESI_CLI_EXTERNAL_MENU
Use external menu: 0=fzf, 1=rofi, 2=dmenu (default: 0).
.TP
.B DESI_CLI_HIST_DIR
History directory (default: $XDG_STATE_HOME/desi\-cli or
$HOME/.local/state/desi\-cli).
.TP
.B DESI_CLI_BRANCH
Git branch for updates (default: master).
.SH NOTES
YouTube extraction may require authentication for some content.
If extraction fails, export cookies from your browser using the
"Get cookies.txt" extension and pass them with \-\-cookies-file.
.SH DEPENDENCIES
yt\-dlp, fzf (or rofi/dmenu), mpv (or vlc/iina/syncplay),
curl, sed, grep, awk.
.SH FILES
.I $HOME/.local/state/desi\-cli/desi\-hsts
.RS
Watch history file.
.RE
